{
    "poem_title": "Ode",
    "author": "Alphonse de Lamartine",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1820",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Peuple ! des crimes de tes pères",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Le ciel punissant tes enfants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "De châtiments héréditaires",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Accablera leurs descendants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à ce qu'une main propice",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Relève l'auguste édifice",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Par qui la terre touche aux cieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et que le zèle et la prière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Dissipent l'indigne poussière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qui couvre l'image des dieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Peuple ! des crimes de tes pères\nLe ciel punissant tes enfants,\nDe châtiments héréditaires\nAccablera leurs descendants,\nJusqu'à ce qu'une main propice\nRelève l'auguste édifice\nPar qui la terre touche aux cieux,\nEt que le zèle et la prière\nDissipent l'indigne poussière\nQui couvre l'image des dieux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Sortez de vos débris antiques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Temples que pleurait Israël ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Relevez-vous, sacrés portiques ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Lévites, montez à l'autel !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Aux sons des harpes de Solyme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Que la renaissante victime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "S'immole sous vos chastes mains ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Et qu'avec les pleurs de la terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Son sang éteigne le tonnerre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Qui gronde encor sur les humains !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sortez de vos débris antiques,\nTemples que pleurait Israël ;\nRelevez-vous, sacrés portiques ;\nLévites, montez à l'autel !\nAux sons des harpes de Solyme,\nQue la renaissante victime\nS'immole sous vos chastes mains ;\nEt qu'avec les pleurs de la terre\nSon sang éteigne le tonnerre\nQui gronde encor sur les humains !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Plein d'une superbe folie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Ce peuple au front audacieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "S'est dit un jour : « Dieu m'humilie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Soyons à nous-mêmes nos dieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Notre intelligence sublime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "A sondé le ciel et l'abîme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Pour y chercher ce grand esprit ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Mais ni dans les flancs de la terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Mais ni dans les feux de la sphère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Son nom pour nous ne fut écrit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Plein d'une superbe folie,\nCe peuple au front audacieux\nS'est dit un jour : « Dieu m'humilie ;\nSoyons à nous-mêmes nos dieux.\nNotre intelligence sublime\nA sondé le ciel et l'abîme\nPour y chercher ce grand esprit ;\nMais ni dans les flancs de la terre,\nMais ni dans les feux de la sphère,\nSon nom pour nous ne fut écrit."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "« Déjà-nous enseignons au monde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "A briser le sceptre des rois ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Déjà notre audace profonde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Se rit du joug usé des lois ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Secouez, malheureux esclaves,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Secouez d'indignes entraves,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Rentrez dans votre liberté !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Mortel ! du jour où tu respires,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Ta loi, c'est ce que tu désires ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Ton devoir, c'est la volupté !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Déjà-nous enseignons au monde\nA briser le sceptre des rois ;\nDéjà notre audace profonde\nSe rit du joug usé des lois ;\nSecouez, malheureux esclaves,\nSecouez d'indignes entraves,\nRentrez dans votre liberté !\nMortel ! du jour où tu respires,\nTa loi, c'est ce que tu désires ;\nTon devoir, c'est la volupté !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "« Ta pensée a franchi l'espace,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Tes calculs précèdent les temps,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "La foudre cède à ton audace,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Les cieux roulent tes chars flottants ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Comme un feu que tout alimente,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Ta raison, sans cesse croissante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "S'étendra sur l'immensité ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Et ta puissance, qu'elle assure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "N'aura de terme et de mesure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Que l'espace et l'éternité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Ta pensée a franchi l'espace,\nTes calculs précèdent les temps,\nLa foudre cède à ton audace,\nLes cieux roulent tes chars flottants ;\nComme un feu que tout alimente,\nTa raison, sans cesse croissante,\nS'étendra sur l'immensité ;\nEt ta puissance, qu'elle assure,\nN'aura de terme et de mesure\nQue l'espace et l'éternité."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "\" Heureux nos fils ! heureux cet âge",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Qui, fécondé par nos leçons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Viendra recueillir l'héritage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Des dogmes que nous lui laissons !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Pourquoi les jalouses années",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Bornent-elles nos destinées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "À de si rapides instants ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "O loi trop injuste et trop dure !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Pour triompher de la nature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Que nous a-t-il manqué ? le temps. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Heureux nos fils ! heureux cet âge\nQui, fécondé par nos leçons,\nViendra recueillir l'héritage\nDes dogmes que nous lui laissons !\nPourquoi les jalouses années\nBornent-elles nos destinées\nÀ de si rapides instants ?\nO loi trop injuste et trop dure !\nPour triompher de la nature\nQue nous a-t-il manqué ? le temps. »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Eh bien, le temps sur vos poussières",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "A peine encore a fait un pas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Sortez, ô mânes de nos pères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Sortez de la nuit du trépas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Venez contempler votre ouvrage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Venez partager de cet âge",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "La gloire et la félicité !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "O race en promesses féconde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Paraissez ! Bienfaiteurs du monde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Voilà votre postérité !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh bien, le temps sur vos poussières\nA peine encore a fait un pas\nSortez, ô mânes de nos pères,\nSortez de la nuit du trépas !\nVenez contempler votre ouvrage,\nVenez partager de cet âge\nLa gloire et la félicité !\nO race en promesses féconde,\nParaissez ! Bienfaiteurs du monde,\nVoilà votre postérité !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Que vois-je ? ils détournent la vue,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Et, se cachant sous leurs lambeaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Leur foule, de honte éperdue,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Fuit et rentre dans les tombeaux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Non, non, restez, ombres coupables ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Auteurs de nos jours déplorables,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Restez ! ce supplice est trop doux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Le ciel, trop lent à vous poursuivre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Devait vous condamner à vivre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Dans le siècle enfanté par vous !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que vois-je ? ils détournent la vue,\nEt, se cachant sous leurs lambeaux,\nLeur foule, de honte éperdue,\nFuit et rentre dans les tombeaux.\nNon, non, restez, ombres coupables ;\nAuteurs de nos jours déplorables,\nRestez ! ce supplice est trop doux.\nLe ciel, trop lent à vous poursuivre.\nDevait vous condamner à vivre\nDans le siècle enfanté par vous !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Où sont-ils, ces jours où la France,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "A la tête des nations,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Se levait comme un astre immense",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Inondant tout de ses rayons ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Parmi nos siècles, siècle unique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "De quel cortège magnifique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "La gloire composait ta cour !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "Semblable au dieu qui nous éclaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 89,
                    "line_text": "Ta grandeur étonnait la terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 90,
                    "line_text": "Dont tes clartés étaient l'amour !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Où sont-ils, ces jours où la France,\nA la tête des nations,\nSe levait comme un astre immense\nInondant tout de ses rayons ?\nParmi nos siècles, siècle unique,\nDe quel cortège magnifique\nLa gloire composait ta cour !\nSemblable au dieu qui nous éclaire,\nTa grandeur étonnait la terre,\nDont tes clartés étaient l'amour !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 91,
                    "line_text": "Toujours les siècles du génie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 92,
                    "line_text": "Sont donc les siècles des vertus !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
